<para id="element-14">
Dividing equation - 4 by equation - 2, we have :
</para>
<para id="element-15">
<equation id="equation-15">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> v </m:mi>
<m:mi> 1i </m:mi>
</m:msub>
