<section id="section-1aa">
<title> Special cases </title>
<para id="element-31">
Here, we discuss some special cases of elastic collision in one dimension :
</para>
<para id="element-32">
<term>1: Collision between equal masses :</term>
</para>
<para id="element-33">In this case, 
