</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-62">The first result reveals that the heavier projectile indeed maintains its initial velocity. 
</para>
<para id="element-63">On the other hand, velocity of the lighter target varies and depends on the combination of initial velocities of both projectile and target. If the target is initially at rest, then 
</para>
<para id="element-64"><m:math display="block">
